title.narrative: VIOLENCE-FREE COMPREHENSIVE PROTECTION SPACES

description.narrative: By 2024, institutions, professionals and communities in prioritized areas and territories have increased their capacities to strengthen spaces for comprehensive protection, free from violence., which contributes to Adolescent Empowerment, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2024, more girls, boys and adolescents from prioritized groups and territories benefit from comprehensive, violence-free prevention and protection services and areas.
